'''ZeroNet'''，中文译名为“'''零网'''”，是一个以[[对等网络|对等网络]]用户为基础构成的类[[互联网|互联网]]的[[去中心化|分布式]][[计算机网络|网络]]，以抗[[审查制度|审查]]为目的，旨在促进[[言論自由|言论自由]]。支持[[IPv4|IPv4]]、[[IPv6|IPv6]]和[[cjdns|cjdns]]协议。ZeroNet的作者位于[[匈牙利|匈牙利]]的[[布达佩斯|布达佩斯]]。ZeroNet默认不提供匿名保护，但用户可以使用[[Tor|Tor]]来隐藏IP地址以达到[[匿名|匿名]]效果。由于[[Tor|Tor]]网络在中国大陆被封禁，用户可能需要前置代理或者VPN才能正常下载初始配置文件。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=https://torrentfreak.com/play-p2p-impossible-shutdown-160301/|title=Play: A P2P Distributed Torrent Site That's Impossible to Shut Down - TorrentFreak|website=TorrentFreak|language=en-US|access-date=2016-03-08|archive-date=2016-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308004610/https://torrentfreak.com/play-p2p-impossible-shutdown-160301/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

ZeroNet使用了[[比特币|比特币]][[密码学|加密技术]]（即[[公开密钥加密|非对称加密]]）和类似于[[BitTorrent_(协议)|BitTorrent]]的网络协议。ZeroNet不具备DHT功能，但可以兼容已有的[[torrent|torrent]] [[tracker|tracker]]服务器。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Kysar|first1=Tom|title=ZeroNet Expands Key Distributed And Anonymous Features|url=http://bravenewcoin.com/news/zeronet-expands-key-distributed-and-anonymous-features/|website=bravenewcoin.com|accessdate=20 September 2015|date=18 March 2015|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924140104/http://bravenewcoin.com/news/zeronet-expands-key-distributed-and-anonymous-features/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Sewell|first1=Chase|title=Can Blockchain Technology Decentralize the Web?|url=http://insidebitcoins.com/news/can-blockchain-technology-decentralize-the-web/28793|website=insidebitcoins.com|accessdate=20 September 2015|date=15 January 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925155542/http://insidebitcoins.com/news/can-blockchain-technology-decentralize-the-web/28793|archivedate=2015年9月25日}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Kumar|first1=Mohit|title=MegaNet — New Decentralized, Non-IP Based and Encrypted Network|url=https://thehackernews.com/2015/02/meganet-decentralized-internet.html|publisher=The Hacker News|accessdate=20 September 2015|date=18 February 2015|archive-date=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925150625/https://thehackernews.com/2015/02/meganet-decentralized-internet.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>现时该平台上托管了很多热门网站，而[[邮件客户端|邮件客户端]]、[[文件管理器|文件管理器]]和新闻客户端等专有功能也为ZeroNet的生态系统增加了价值。<ref>{{cite web|title=ZeroNet: A Perfect Match For Bitcoin?|url=https://easterndaily.com/zeronet-perfect-match-bitcoin/|author=Peter Ngigi|publisher=easterndaily|date=2017-03-17|access-date=2017-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170325112819/https://easterndaily.com/zeronet-perfect-match-bitcoin/|archive-date=2017-03-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

